WEBVTT

00:00.050 --> 00:03.345
Here are some phrases you can use to describe the weather.

00:05.099 --> 00:06.163
What's the weather like?

00:07.932 --> 00:09.043
The weather's fine.

00:10.827 --> 00:12.049
It's a sunny day today.

00:13.838 --> 00:15.310
It's been raining all day.

00:17.038 --> 00:18.567
It's freezing cold.

00:20.113 --> 00:21.553
It looks like it's going to rain.

00:23.417 --> 00:24.820
It's pouring out there.

00:26.648 --> 00:27.642
The sun's come out.

00:29.227 --> 00:30.746
What a nice day!

00:32.442 --> 00:33.961
That sounds like thunder.

